{
  "0": "Alignment & Safety Techniques:",
  "1": "Alignment is the process of ensuring an",
  "2": "AI model's behavior aligns with human",
  "3": "values and expectations, making it",
  "4": "helpful and harmless. The most",
  "5": "prominent technique is Reinforcement",
  "6": "Learning from Human Feedback",
  "7": "(RLHF), where a \"reward model\" trained",
  "8": "on human preferences guides the AI's",
  "9": "learning process, often using an",
  "10": "algorithm like Proximal Policy",
  "11": "Optimization (PPO) for stability. Simpler",
  "12": "alternatives have emerged, such as",
  "13": "Direct Preference Optimization (DPO),",
  "14": "which bypasses the need for a separate",
  "15": "reward model, and Kahneman-Tversky",
  "16": "Optimization (KTO), which simplifies",
  "17": "data collection further. To ensure safe",
